#setosa를 세모, versicolor를 네모, virginica를 동그라미로 표시
markers=['^', 's', 'o']
#pca_component_1 을 x축, pc_component_2를 y축으로 scatter plot 수행. 
for i, marker in enumerate(markers):
    x_axis_data = principalDf[principalDf['found_age_6']==i]['principal component1']
    y_axis_data = principalDf[principalDf['found_age_6']==i]['principal component2']
    plt.scatter(x_axis_data, y_axis_data, marker=marker,label=iris.target_names[i])
plt.legend()
plt.xlabel('principal component1')
plt.ylabel('principal component2')
plt.show()
